# albumproject
This website lets you create and view photo albums
Run the command "node server.js" on command line.
Go to localhost:3001/login, you will see login page of the website. If you are an existing user enter your email and password to see homepage,else click on register and register on the website by filling out the form.
Once you are on homepage, click on the plus sign to add new album. A pop-up form will appear asking for album name and coverimage,fill out the form and after clicking on submit you will see your newly added albums.
